g_keys\": [\"context canceled\", \"rpc error\", \"transport is closing\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Multiple RPC calls from frontend services are being canceled (context canceled) or encountering transport issues (transport is closing).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"\\\"could not retrieve product: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\n基于收集到的指标数据，我现在对故障期间的系统状态进行分析。从指标数据可以看出，故障期间出现了多个服务级别的异常。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"request\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"请求量急剧下降（request从6765降至132，变化率192.34%）同时出现错误率上升（error_ratio从0%升至9.38%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-1的request指标中位数从6765降至132，error_ratio从0%升至9.38%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-0\", \n      \"reason\": \"请求量显著下降（request从582降至16，变化率189.3%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-0的request指标中位数从582降至16\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"多个Pod出现高错误率（error_ratio和client_error_ratio高达60-65.6%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-2 error_ratio 60%，shippingservice-1 error_ratio 65.6%，shippingservice-0 error_ratio 58.75%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"多个Pod出现高错误率（error_ratio和client_error_ratio高达46.72-50%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-2 error_ratio 46.72%，cartservice-1 error_ratio 50%，cartservice-0 error_ratio 16.8%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"所有Pod出现高错误率（error_ratio和server_error_ratio高达27.66-35.48%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0 error_ratio 27.66%，frontend-1 error_ratio 35.48%，frontend-2 error_ratio 33.33%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-0, productcatalogservice-1, frontend-0, frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU使用率降至0或接近0（pod_cpu_usage变化率100-200%）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice-0 pod_cpu_usage从0.01降至0，frontend-2从0.04降至0，frontend-0从0.05降至0，productcatalogservice-1从0.05降至0\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\n基于收集到的追踪数据，我已经完成了对故障时间段的分析。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"frontend->productcatalogservice\", \"error_ratio\", \"productcatalogservice->tidb\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend调用productcatalogservice的延迟异常激增：GetProduct操作从正常11秒增加到56秒（5倍），ListProducts操作从正常2秒增加到58秒（29倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\", \n      \"evidence\": \"大量context canceled错误（超过380次）和transport is closing错误（17次），表明productcatalogservice无法正常处理请求\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端服务出现大量HTTP 500错误（479次），作为上游服务受到下游productcatalogservice故障的直接影响\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现分析\n\n### 1. **根因定位**\n- **最下游异常**: `frontend->productcatalogservice` 调用链中，productcatalogservice出现严重延迟和错误\n- **错误起始点**: productcatalogservice是调用链中第一个报错的服务，表现为大量`context canceled`和`transport is closing`错误\n\n### 2. **延迟分析**\n- **GetProduct操作**: 正常11秒 → 异常56秒（延迟增加5倍）\n- **ListProducts操作**: 正常2秒 → 异常58秒（延迟增加29倍）\n- 延迟倍数远超2.0阈值，属于显著延迟\n\n### 3. **错误传播路径**\n```\nfrontend (HTTP 500错误) ← productcatalogservice (context canceled/transport is closing)\n```\n- 前端服务出现HTTP 500错误是因为下游productcatalogservice无法正常响应\n- 推荐服务也受到轻微影响，但程度较轻\n\n### 4. **故障影响范围**\n- **主要影响**: frontend服务的所有三个实例（frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2）\n- **次要影响**: recommendationservice\n- **未受影响**: checkoutservice、cartservice等未出现明显异常\n\n**结论**: productcatalogservice是本次系统故障的根因组件，其严重的性能退化导致了前端服务的级联故障。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_ana